title: Song of the Duck Dance (c)
lyrics_translation: The first flowers are blooming, so we are glad.

title: Song of the Duck Dance (d)
lyrics_translation: Lively, lively. We are lots of people.

title: Circle Dance Song (a)
lyrics_translation: There is a cloud in the heavens.

title: Song of a Jumping Dance
lyrics_translation: I jump down and dance, then I jump back up and dance.

title: Song of the Two Boys Who Went for Clover
Look at the Poppy Flowers, Growing Fine
The Two Girls on the Bridge
lyrics_translation: Put the two girls on the bridge so the crow cannot get them.

title: Closing Song of the Adolescence Ceremony
lyrics_translation: This is the last song. Some day we will sing it for another girl.

title: The Neglected Wife Goes Away
lyrics_translation: I am a fine-looking woman; still I am running with my tears.

title: The Neglected Wife Is Pursued by Her Husband
lyrics_translation: Wait for your property, you two. Wait for your property.

title: The Gray Squirrels and the Fire
lyrics_translation: We come after the fire to put it out.

title: Song of a Hunter
lyrics_translation: We have been hunting today. We are loaded down. The feathers are heavy.

title: A Rabbit Is Going North
lyrics_translation: I am hopping along. I am going north. I will get there after a while.

title: A Goose Laments His Lost Brother
lyrics_translation: How about it? My brother died. How about it? My brother died.

title: Lullaby
lyrics_translation: The swallow (to'lip) is singing for the baby.
